==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loper
<hw>Lop"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or
that which, lopes; esp., a horse that lopes.</def>
<mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Rope Making)</fld> <def>A swivel at one end of a
ropewalk, used in laying the strands.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lophine</ent>⟦br⟧
